delta_g <- tmp_data %>% select(OID, slide_id, scene_id, unique_identifier, predicted.celltype, predicted.celltype3, ND.REC, survival_group, sample_interval_days) %>% filter(!is.na(predicted.celltype3),!predicted.celltype3%in%"BLANK") %>% mutate(predicted.celltype3 = ifelse(predicted.celltype3%in%c('CD163','CD206','M2',"M2 (CD163+/CD206+ DP)"),'M2',predicted.celltype3)) %>% group_by(unique_identifier, ND.REC, predicted.celltype3) %>% 
  summarise(N = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  group_by(unique_identifier, ND.REC) %>% 
  mutate(M = sum(N)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  mutate(P = round(100*N/M, 2))

delta_g <- delta_g %>% 
  select(-N,-M) %>% 
  spread(ND.REC,P, fill=0) %>% 
  mutate(P = REC-ND)
one <- test %>% filter(is.na(tumor))
delta_g <- delta_g %>% select(-ND,-REC) %>% spread(predicted.celltype3,P, fill = 0)
delta_g <- delta_g %>% filter(!unique_identifier%in%unique(one$unique_identifier))

sur <- df_exp_design_scenes %>% select(unique_identifier, sample_interval_days,ND.REC) %>% unique() %>% 
  group_by(unique_identifier,ND.REC) %>% summarize(sample_interval_days2 = min(sample_interval_days)) %>% ungroup() %>% filter(ND.REC=="REC")


delta_g <- delta_g %>% left_join(sur %>% select(unique_identifier,sample_interval_days2) %>% unique())

delta_test <- sample_n(delta_g, round(dim(delta_g)[1]*0.1))

delta_train <- delta_g %>% filter(!unique_identifier%in%delta_test$unique_identifier)
model<- lm(formula = sample_interval_days2 ~ AC+CD11C+CD163HLADR+CD44+CD8Eact+CD8Fact+CD8mem+CD8mix+CD8naive+CD8Tex+DC+EOMES+GRB7+HLADR+HSP70+KI67+M2+MES+NPC+OPC+OTHER+PD1+PD1HSP70+PDL1+THeff+THmem+THnaive+Treg, data = delta_train)

summary(model)
a <- predict(model, newdata = delta_test)
